Name: Yamaha Tyros5
Description: The Tyros5 is Yamaha's ultimate performance keyboard, with outstanding sounds, enhanced DSP effects and realistic accompaniment styles. Experience a level of authenticity like no other instrument, it's like being backed by the world's finest musicians.

Name: Boss DR-3 Dr Rhythm Drum Machine
Description: With the DR-3 Dr. Rhythm, guitarists and songwriters can add incredible-sounding drums to their music. This ultra-affordable drum machine includes some of BOSS' best acoustic and electronic drum kits and a selection of bass sounds.
